cs.GR, cs.CV, cs.CG, cs.MM, cs.AI 

The paper proposes a modification to a muscle-based system for facial capture, which involves both 3D geometry and image processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.GR (Graphics), which deals with 3D modeling and rendering. The paper also involves computer vision techniques for facial pose estimation, which suggests the category cs.CV (Computer Vision). Additionally, the paper involves computational geometry for shape matching, which suggests the category cs.CG (Computational Geometry). The paper also involves machine learning techniques for optimization and learning-based approaches, which suggests the category cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper involves artificial intelligence techniques for semantic interpretability, which suggests the category cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
